        <name>on_properties_changed</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This callback will be invoked when <ref refid="struct_m_l_power_manager_property_data" kindref="compound">MLPowerManagerPropertyData</ref> of a component changes. Only the properties that have changed will be returned, the component may support additional properties which values were not returned. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">properties</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="struct_m_l_power_manager_property_data" kindref="compound">MLPowerManagerPropertyData</ref> struct encapsulating the properties changed. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">user_data</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>User data as passed to the <ref refid="group___power_manager_1gafd4bc89d539a0de46b072fc8d2f06e98" kindref="member">MLPowerManagerSetCallbacks</ref>. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
